            <description><![CDATA[过去的30年里，累计救助了175万人次，没错，就靠“一腔热血”！在深圳，超过534万人次，无偿献血1068吨。他们点亮了别人的生命，深圳也用1000架无人机，为这群热血的人将夜空点亮，愿这片星光永远灿烂，照亮更多坠入了黑夜的人们<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抱一抱]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/co_a1hug-f3910d0e88.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抱一抱]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/co_a1hug-f3910d0e88.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抱一抱]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/co_a1hug-f3910d0e88.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%83%8F%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B7%E7%83%AD%E8%A1%8030%E5%B9%B4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%83%8F%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B7%E7%83%AD%E8%A1%8030%E5%B9%B4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#像你一样热血30年#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%8C%AE%E8%A1%80%E8%80%85%E6%97%A5%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#世界献血者日#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4912575268454437" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hexuzy4f1sj21hc0u0kad.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/OduWuN97gx086eo6k02Y01041201t8DG0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1686749511&amp;ssig=j6uXgba737&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/eZuHJ3Flgx086eo5Ixja01041200MjBT0E010.mp4?la